      <abstract>
        <p>A new heterocycle 2-(3-methoxy-4-hexadecanoyloxyphenyl)benzothiazole was synthesized and its IR, <sup>1</sup>H NMR, <sup>13</sup>C NMR and MS spectroscopic data are presented.</p>
      </abstract>
